#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.add.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.add"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:1 of
msgid "Add arguments element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素相加参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:3 maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:7 of
msgid ""
"The tensors to be added.  If ``x1.shape != x2.shape``, they must be "
"broadcastable to a common shape (which may be the shape of one or the "
"other)."
msgstr ""
"要相加的张量。如果 ``x1.shape != x2.shape``，它们必须可以广播到一个共同的"
"形状（可能是其中一个的形状）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有输入广播到的形状。如果未提供或为 "
"`None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:21 of
msgid ""
"**add** -- The sum of `x1` and `x2`, element-wise.  Returns a scalar if "
"both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**add** -- `x1` 和 `x2` 的逐元素之和。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回"
"标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.add.add:27 of
msgid "Equivalent to `x1` + `x2` in terms of tensor broadcasting."
msgstr "在张量广播方面等价于 `x1` + `x2`。"

